            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced red onion</strong> to a bowl with the <strong>red wine vinegar </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong></p><p>Chop the <strong>chestnut mushrooms</strong> into quarters</p><p>Drain and rinse the <strong>black beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1632824463677-x200.jpg",
