    {
      "instruction": "<p>Brush the <strong>tortillas</strong> with a little <strong>olive oil</strong> on each side and season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> tortillas</strong> to a baking tray and place a second baking tray on top to weigh them down slightly</p><p>Put the stacked baking trays in the oven in the oven for 12-15 min or until the tortillas are golden and crisp – these are <strong>crispy tortillas</strong></p>",
