    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a medium, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped mushrooms</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for a further 5-6 min or until tender – these are you <strong>smoky mushrooms</strong></p>",
