    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the black beans have softened, season with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper </strong>and mash them to a coarse paste – these are your <strong>refried beans</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>yoghurt </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>garlic yoghurt</strong></p><p>Cut the remaining <strong>lime</strong> into wedges</p>",
