    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your tostadas, top the <strong>crispy tortillas</strong> with the <strong>refried beans</strong>, <strong>smoky mushrooms</strong>, <strong>avocado salsa</strong>, <strong>quick-pickled red onion</strong> and <strong>garlic yoghurt</strong></p><p>Garnish with the<strong> remaining chopped</strong> <strong>coriander </strong>and a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
